{"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"group":[{"node":{"id":"75ead3e4-25c9-5f8d-912e-71d393ab7469","fields":{"slug":"learn-javascript-through-stackoverflow"},"frontmatter":{"tags":["JavaScript"],"templateKey":"blog-post","slug":"learn-javascript-through-stackoverflow","id":null,"title":"如何利用 Stack Overflow 高效學習 JavaScript？","url":"learn-javascript-through-stackoverflow","date":"2019-03-15T02:38:23.251Z","description":"帶著問題去學習，會比單純看書的效果好得多。而 Stack Overflow 網站雲集世界上不同程序員遇到的問題，我們可以透過它來高效學習技能，比如說前端工程師的技能：JavaScript。","headerImage":"https://i.imgur.com/VvGbog9.jpg"}}},{"node":{"id":"baa14d35-cadc-55c8-809b-dea34cd4446c","fields":{"slug":"/how-to-deploy-nodejs-application-via-zeit-free-plan"},"frontmatter":{"tags":["ZEIT","NOW","React","免費","實用"],"templateKey":"blog-post","slug":"/how-to-deploy-nodejs-application-via-zeit-free-plan","id":"a13adea8-84f6-5965-904e-9a2f5a5f1c1e","title":"如何透過 ZEIT 方便快捷地部署免費的 Node.js 項目？","url":"/how-to-deploy-nodejs-application-via-zeit-free-plan","date":"2019-03-04T01:00:00.000Z","description":"ZEIT 平台提供了免費的網站空間平台給開發者，我們可以透過 ZEIT 平台來部署 Node.js, Express.js, Koa.js 等應用。如果你有寫過 Node.js 應用，又想找個免費空間部署這些應用的話，那麼 ZEIT 會是一個不錯的選擇。","headerImage":"https://i.imgur.com/Lgfa2Eu.png"}}},{"node":{"id":"ca2b4243-bafb-5265-9aa2-0c3e739519cc","fields":{"slug":"/why-import-react-from-react-in-a-functional-component"},"frontmatter":{"tags":["React","Babel","JSX","閱讀","前端"],"templateKey":"blog-post","slug":"/why-import-react-from-react-in-a-functional-component","id":null,"title":"為什麼函數式組件需要引進 React？","url":"/why-import-react-from-react-in-a-functional-component","date":"2019-02-26T09:44:05.963Z","description":"在編寫組件時，最讓我迷惑的是在我編寫純函數組件，為什麼沒有在代碼裡面調用 React 都需要導入 React。經過一番調研，我發現是因為 JSX 轉譯的設定。不過，人是比較懶惰的，透過安裝 babel-plugin-react-require 插件，達到自動導入 React 的效果。這篇文章將會講述我的調研經歷和一點反思。","headerImage":"https://i.imgur.com/3GRiphI.png"}}},{"node":{"id":"3c94e08e-cdd9-5fca-a5fc-dcba093fe032","fields":{"slug":"/how-to-use-react-to-render-markdown-articles"},"frontm